H3.text: What boy with a girl's name was sung about by Johnny Cash. Sue

A4.text: A Boy Named Sue is a song written by Shel Silverstein and made famous by Johnny Cash.

A5.text: The song tells the tale of a young man's quest for revenge on a father who abandoned him at three years of age and whose only contribution to his entire life was giving him a guitar and naming him Sue.
